        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName> Dei gracia
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Quia divini muneris nutu regni
                        gubernacula reguntur, nullaque potestas nisi a Deo procedit, pro certo
                        regalem omnino (eius) decet excellenciam, ut ea que, Deo largiente,
                        suscepit, pro suorum fidelium commodo impartire studeat, ut dum eorum
                        precibus benignitatis sue aures acommodat eos in suo obsequi devociores
                        efficiat, insuper ab eterno remuneratore premia sine fine mansura percipiat.
                        Idcirco omnium sancte Dei Ecclesie nostrorumque fidelium presencium scilicet
                        ac futurorum comperiat industria, eo quod <persName key="#Abbots"
                            >Iohannes</persName> vir probus ac prudentissimus medicus noster <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/120">monasterii Sancte
                            Cristine</orgName> prope <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/139"
                            >curtem nostram Ollonam</geogName> sive per <persName
                            key="#Consiliarius_regis #Bishops" ref="#people/58">Petrum</persName>
                        venerabilem <rs key="#Bishops">episcopum</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Consiliarius_regis">Restaldum</persName> et per <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Consiliarius_regis">Ascherium</persName> illustrem
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionem</rs> summos <rs
                            key="#Consiliarius_regis">consciliarios</rs> nostros expetiis clemenciam
                        nostram, ut ei quandam <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >curtem</rs> iuris regni nostri nomine <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/141">Bellamium</geogName> in <rs key="#Comitatus"
                            >comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/142">Aquinense</geogName> cum
                        omnibus pertinenciis et adiacenciis suis in integrum, <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >casis</rs> videlicet, <rs
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >ortis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >pratis, pascuis, campis, cultis et incultis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >silvis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >arboribus pomiferis et impomiferis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >montibus, valibus, planitiebus, ripis, rupinis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >aquis et aquarum decursibus</rs>, seu <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >molendinis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Slave"
                            >servis quoque et ancillis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Aldius"
                            >aldionibus et aldianis</rs> concedere dignaremur. Cuius precibus
                        libenter adquiescentes hoc nostrum preceptum fieri iussimus, per quod
                        predictam curtem cum omnibus pertinentiis et adiacentiis suis prefato
                        Iohanni abbati vel successoribus ipsius <rs
                            key="#Houses #Natural_landscape #Curtes #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Mills #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Allocation_to_churches #Aldius #Slave"
                            >proprietario iure</rs> concedimus et perdonamus, ut habeat, teneat
                        atque possideat, tam ipse quam et successores eius, faciatque exinde
                        quicquid eius decreverit animus. Confirmamus ei potestate tenendi,
                        possidendi, donandi, vendendi, commutandi seu in qualibet ipsius loci
                        necessitate alienandi, remota cuiuslibet publice potestatis inquietudine ac
                        molestatione. Confirmamus insuper atque concedimus eidem Iohanni abbati
                        eiusque successoribus terram circa ipsum monasterium positam imperatorum,
                        regum seu quorumlibet potestatum fideli renovacione collatam cum tutela
                        servanda, ab oriente <rs
                            key="#Lakes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >lacus</rs> qui dicitur Sussinate cum tota
                            <placeName>Vallinata</placeName> in integrum usque in Padum, a meridie
                            <rs
                            key="#Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Ports"
                            >portus qui vocatur Novus</rs> cum rochalibus supera, ab occidente vero
                        a curte nostra Ollona dividitur, a septentrione igitur <placeName>terra
                                <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53">Sancti Systi</orgName> que
                            nuncupatur Yberni</placeName> et extenditur usque ad <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvium Lambrum</rs> et <placeName>Victumlongum</placeName> atque
                            <placeName>Castellum Desertum</placeName> et usque ad
                            <placeName>fontanam Sancti Ambrosii</placeName> et
                            <placeName>Brionem</placeName> et totus insuper <placeName
                            ref="#places/277">Monsmallus</placeName> usque in predicta Vallinata. Si
                        quis autem contra hoc nostrum preceptum quandocumque insurgere temptaverit,
                        sciat se compositurum triginta libras auri obrizi, medietatem palacio nostro
                        et medietatem prefato abbati eiusque successoribus. Ut autem ab omnibus
                        verius credatur et diligencius observetur, manu propria subtus confirmavimus
                        et anuli nostri impressione insigniri iussimus. Signum domni Berengarii
                        serenissimi regis. <persName key="#Notary">Restaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> iussione regia ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/58">Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellari</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Dat.
                        Kal. Decembris, anno incarnationis Domini DCCCXCVIII, anno vero regni domani
                        Berengarii gloriosissimi regis XII, indicione secunda. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/191">Regia</placeName> civitate. In Dei nomine feliciter,
                        amen. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
